title: Readout of Vice President Mike Pence’s Telephone Call with Prime Minister Scott Morrison of Australia – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
May 19, 2019
Vice President Mike Pence spoke by phone last night with Prime Minister of the Commonwealth of Australia Scott Morrison, congratulating him on his Coalition’s win in the Australian Federal elections. He reaffirmed the strong bilateral relationship and enduring alliance between the United States and Australia.
